data.title: The Ultimate Lash Boss Bundle
data.meta_description: If for any reason the kit does not automatically discount when added to your cart, at checkout you may use the code LLAFREEKIT for your free kit with purchase of the ULBB!
data.text:
The ULBB has elevated my experience and dynamics of lashing! I was a struggling artist in my first year of lashing. Although I knew I found my passion, I found it hard to have hope and see everything through! Lanna Lashes helped me find my brand, build clientele and truly stick out in this industry. I went from getting 1 new client a week to having 5+ a week (my clientele is almost full now). Every time I post something on instagram I have a new appointment request! My favorite thing about Lanna is her mindset. I feel like my mindset has truly changed being a follower! This career is carving me into the person I have always wanted to become and Lanna Lashes helped me a lot with that. Forever grateful for this experience and I’m so excited to see where this journey takes me with Lanna Lashes!! <3

I purchased the Ultimate Lash Boss Bundle and this was the best decision I ever made. I went into it not knowing anything and now I am able to do classic, volume, and am still practicing wispy. Everytime i wanted to refresh my memory I would go back to a video Lanna posted or even sometimes get inspiration from their instagram. I learned so much not only about extensions but the safety and lash health of a client. I only use Lannas products and clients love the glue. I never have red eyes, irritation, or burning. Overall the Ultimate Lash Boss Bundle has helped my grow not only in my confidence but also I’m my mindset as a beginner lash tech.

After a month of thinking I finally gave in and bought it and I never regretted getting it! It has everything that I need. I’m no beginner but I haven’t done lashes for a year after getting certified from my previous instructor which makes me a beginner but this course really helped me set my mind and goal! Beauty is really my passion. This course is definitely a must have and worth it in my own experience. It helped me determine the importance of the eye shapes and tailoring sets. Also, helped me become more creative and confident as her techniques are really straightforward and amazing. I kinda combine what I am learning from her techniques along with my own techniques. I’m so excited to what this course could bring my lashing career and it definitely increases knowledge. ❤️
